            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="p">
            I develop comprehensive Behaviour Support Plans (BSPs) that align with NDIS requirements and 
            focus on improving quality of life while addressing behaviours of concern through positive, 
            evidence-based strategies.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="h3">What's Included:</h3>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li><strong>Person-Centered Planning:</strong> Focus on individual goals, preferences, and strengths</li>
            <li><strong>Proactive Strategies:</strong> Environmental modifications and skill-building approaches</li>
            <li><strong>Reactive Strategies:</strong> Safe and dignified responses to behaviours of concern</li>
            <li><strong>Skill Development:</strong> Teaching alternative behaviours and life skills</li>
            <li><strong>Restrictive Practice Documentation:</strong> If required, comprehensive restrictive practice assessments</li>
            <li><strong>Implementation Guidelines:</strong> Clear, practical guidance for support teams</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="service-approach">
            <h3 class="h3">My Approach:</h3>
            <div class="approach-pillars">
              <div class="pillar">
                <div class="pillar-icon">üéØ</div>
                <h4>Strength-Based</h4>
                <p>Building on individual capabilities and interests</p>
              </div>
              <div class="pillar">
                <div class="pillar-icon">üè†</div>
                <h4>Quality of Life Focus</h4>
                <p>Improving overall wellbeing and life satisfaction</p>
              </div>
              <div class="pillar">
                <div class="pillar-icon">ü§ù</div>
                <h4>Collaborative</h4>
                <p>Working closely with all stakeholders</p>
              </div>
