          <ul class="service-features">
            <li><strong>Team Training:</strong> Comprehensive training for support workers and family members</li>
            <li><strong>Coaching Sessions:</strong> Regular coaching to build confidence and competence</li>
            <li><strong>Progress Monitoring:</strong> Systematic tracking of plan effectiveness</li>
            <li><strong>Plan Reviews:</strong> Regular reviews and adjustments as needed</li>
            <li><strong>Crisis Support:</strong> Additional support during challenging periods</li>
            <li><strong>Documentation Support:</strong> Assistance with data collection and reporting</li>
          </ul>
          
