        </div>
        
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <h4>Dual Diagnosis</h4>
          <p>Behaviour support for individuals with both disability and mental health considerations</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <h4>Transition Support</h4>
          <p>Supporting individuals through major life transitions (school to adult services, housing changes, etc.)</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <h4>Forensic Disability</h4>
